result.name: nhs-workforce-turnover
result.notes:
Annual turnover figures, by Health Education England regions, for NHS Hospital and Community Health Services (HCHS) staff.

Prior to June 2013, the data is reported at Strategic Health Authority level.

organization.name: nhs-digital
organization.title: NHS Digital
organization.description:
NHS Digital is the national provider of information, data and IT systems for health and social care.

It was previously called 'The Health and Social Care Information Centre (HSCIC)'
